      • getBusinessObjectDataNotificationRegistrationKeysByNotificationFilter

        List<NotificationRegistrationKey> getBusinessObjectDataNotificationRegistrationKeysByNotificationFilter(BusinessObjectDataNotificationFilter businessObjectDataNotificationFilter)
        Gets a list of keys for all existing business object data notification registrations that match the specified business object data notification filter parameters.
        Parameters:
        businessObjectDataNotificationFilter - the filter for the business object data notification. Only the following four filter parameters are used to match the business object data notification registrations:

        • the namespace of the business object definition (required, case-insensitive)
        • the name of the business object definition (required, case-insensitive)
        • the usage of the business object format (optional, case-insensitive)
        • the file type of the business object format (optional, case-insensitive)
        Returns:
        the list of business object data notification registration keys

      • getBusinessObjectDataNotificationRegistrations

        List<BusinessObjectDataNotificationRegistrationEntity> getBusinessObjectDataNotificationRegistrations(String notificationEventTypeCode,
                                                                                                      BusinessObjectDataKey businessObjectDataKey,
                                                                                                      String newBusinessObjectDataStatus,
                                                                                                      String oldBusinessObjectDataStatus,
                                                                                                      String notificationRegistrationStatus)
        Retrieves a list of business object data notification registration entities that match given input parameters.
        Parameters:
        notificationEventTypeCode - the notification event type code (case-insensitive)
        businessObjectDataKey - the business object data key (case-insensitive)
        newBusinessObjectDataStatus - the new business object data status (case-insensitive)
        oldBusinessObjectDataStatus - the old (previous) business object data status (case-insensitive). This parameter will be null for business object data registration
        notificationRegistrationStatus - the status of the notification registration (case-insensitive)
        Returns:
        the list of business object data notification entities
